high_descs: Move towards toilet to the right of the sink
Pick up toilet roll from off the toilet
Move away from the sink a few feet
Open sink cabinet and place roll inside before closing the door
Move closer to the right side of the sink
Pick up empty toilet paper roll from the ground
Move back away from the sink cabinet
Open cabinet and place roll inside and close door
anns.task_desc: Put the toilet paper rolls inside the sink cabinet

high_descs: Locate the toilet, find the toilet paper roll on the back of the toilet.
Pick the toilet paper roll up.
Go to the cabinets to the left of the toilet.
Open the second cabinet door from the right.
Place the toilet paper roll upright near the middle of the cabinet, close the the cabinet door.
Go to the area between the cabinets and the toilet, pick up the empty toilet paper tube behind the toilet brush.
Go to the cabinets to the left of the toilet, open the second cabinet door from the right.
Place the toilet paper tube upright to the left of the full toilet paper roll, close the cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Place the toilet paper roll and empty tube in the cabinet.

high_descs: look down at the toilet a bit
grab the toilet paper off the top of the toilet in front of you
back up a bit to then face the bathroom sink
place the toilet paper in the cabinet below the sink
move forwards a bit towards the toilet
grab the toilet paper tube off of the floor next to the toilet
back up a bit again to then face the bathroom sink again
place the yellow tube in the cabinet underneath the sink
anns.task_desc: place the toilet paper roll with the toilet paper in the bathroom sink cabinet
